{"tid":1872132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班臭閪話示威者令香港經濟差 中美貿易戰令中國經濟差","createTime":"2020-02-10T01:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T23:04:08.000Z","uid":74778,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7a87342d4aa61fabb4ae3e94bf239d61b6d592","tid":1872132,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T01:56:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後搞撚死個經濟嘅係自己大陸人！我話撚知係係食蝙蝠定化武，總之都係中國人劣根性！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n食蝙蝠戇撚鳩死不足惜，根本唔係食物又走去食，<span style=\"color: blue;\">SARS已經講過咪撚再食野味</span>，武漢喺中國中心，交通樞紐，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">佢老母臭閪夠撚膽死喺大車站隔離搞野味批發！僥倖心理！</span></strong>仆街中國人快撚啲死曬佢！<br />\n<br />\n造化武就仲仆街。你話美國夠有鬼鬼祟祟造化武... 咁又唔見人地洩漏？！屌鳩大陸啲廠！閪至造建築材料，專業至化武，都係咁撚求撚其其。幾萬人中招，幾千人死，一洩漏幾撚大鑊，都可以洩漏。仲<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>成日同人講和平和平，平就唔撚洗化武啦，屌你老母習近平！恥爽！死仆街！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港衰就仲撚戇鳩，成撚日好似柒下柒下咁。大陸嘅大方向又唔撚知，成日就係到捕風捉影斷鳩估大陸想點然後就<span style=\"color: blue;\">淨係識諗擦鞋</span>。<br />\n<br />\n由69反送中，大陸無叫你老母臭特區硬推條例，又走去硬推，追撚含。含到鳩支媽碌，台灣都輸鳩埋，都仲係咁，搞撚到<span style=\"color: blue;\">台灣人香港人都憎鳩你，大陸又因為香港政府含得唔舒服又憎鳩埋你。</span><br />\n<br />\n到肺炎，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">完全無國際城市嘅能力，成班官好似弱能咁撚樣</span></strong>，<em>關:唔係唔封不過無需要封或者未有需要咁快封</em>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">完全唔知佢嗡乜柒。</span><em>口罩:唔需要搶，政府會有方法去令巿場有足夠供應，不過喺採購過程面對困難，希望巿民提供方法比政府採購。</em>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">我真係完全唔知佢嗡乜撚野。</span><br />\n<br />\n大佬，你要刷鞋嘅對象食緊屎，你仲等佢order？<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>你面前有700萬個問題，5個訴求，清清楚楚</strong></span>，搞撚掂你咪返去邀功囉，你搞撚掂香港又唔會唔放過你。搞到上又唔係人，下又唔係人。<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">完全無決策力，完全無遠見無planning。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港政府仲管乜撚野丫<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港獨立，唯一出路。</span></span></em>"},{"pid":"4c2e16ebfe7bb08f4c322fbc044092c266964fab","tid":1872132,"uid":49004,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"老母仲係話美國佬故意播毒<br />\n冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cbfbd9fc59fdc073c32417e9c68895ef81cbd6","tid":1872132,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:01:31.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7a81f075a5ffd680c5c176127c93edd837fbdac1","tid":1872132,"uid":149575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"傻鳩廢老點都唔化架啦<br />\n望佢地中肺炎好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b44073a128f32bdd93354a39b2d51f167bb1695","tid":1872132,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:07:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n你知唔知終共hack咗來自三十幾個國家、幾十間 global telecoms 至少七年，竊取了大量 data?? </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191215181157/https://siliconangle.com/2019/06/25/data-stolen-global-telcos-suspected-chinese-hacking-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20191215181157%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fsiliconangle.com%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2Fdata-stolen-global-telcos-suspected-chinese-hacking-campaign&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3a70f9d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20191215181157/https://siliconangle.com/2019/06/25/data-stolen-global-telcos-suspected-chinese-hacking-campaign</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想睇吓點可以阻到終共 track 你？即刻撳入嚟睇:</span></span></strong><br />\n唔想再有手足被黑警自殺？用呢4個apps! (啱所有人用，尤其前線手足)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1864933/page/7?ref=sharer&amp;post=172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thre